 6.8.0-124-generic #124~22.04.1-Ubuntu SMP PREEMPT_DYNAMIC Tue May 26 21:05:19
 UTC  x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux  15:40:53 up 36 min,  1 user,  load
